Run deterministic checks relevant to testing:
- lint when test changes touch linted code
- typecheck when test or app code changes can affect types
- unit or integration tests when available
- build when the changed behavior can affect build output
- E2E when the change is browser-heavy or server-component-heavy and the repo supports it

Return:
- test files changed
- required test layer by change type
- what was tested
- what passed
- what failed
- whether failures look new or pre-existing
- any explicit waiver rationale for missing automated coverage
